@startuml ContractorPro System Flow
!theme cerulean-outline
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title **ContractorPro - Intelligent Construction Business Automation**

actor Contractor as C
actor Client as CL
database Database as DB
component "Email System" as EMAIL
component "File Storage" as FS

package "Core Workflows" {
    rectangle "Lead Management" as LEAD {
        (New Lead Entry) as NewLead
        (Follow-up Tracking) as FollowUp
        (Lead Conversion) as Convert
    }
    
    rectangle "Estimate System" as EST {
        (Template Selection) as Template
        (Cost Calculation) as Calc
        (Professional Email) as EstEmail
    }
    
    rectangle "Job Management" as JOB {
        (Job Creation) as NewJob
        (Progress Tracking) as Progress
        (Contract Generation) as Contract
    }
    
    rectangle "Photo Automation" as PHOTO {
        (Photo Upload) as Upload
        (Milestone Detection) as Milestone
        (Auto Notification) as Notify
    }
}

' Lead Management Flow
C --> NewLead : Manual entry\n(name, email, project type)
NewLead --> DB : Store lead data
NewLead --> FollowUp : Set reminder dates
FollowUp --> Convert : When ready
Convert --> NewJob : Create project

' Estimate Flow
C --> Template : Select project type\n(Kitchen, Bathroom, etc.)
Template --> Calc : Auto-populate costs\n+ overhead + profit
Calc --> EstEmail : Send professional quote
EstEmail --> EMAIL : Automated delivery
EstEmail --> CL : Receive estimate
CL --> Convert : If accepted

' Job Management Flow
NewJob --> DB : Store project details
NewJob --> Contract : Generate agreement
Contract --> Progress : Track milestones

' Photo Automation Flow
C --> Upload : Upload progress photo\n+ milestone %
Upload --> FS : Store image file
Upload --> Milestone : Check if milestone
Milestone --> Notify : Auto-generate email
Notify --> EMAIL : Send to client
EMAIL --> CL : Receive update

' Database interactions
LEAD --> DB
EST --> DB
JOB --> DB
PHOTO --> DB

note right of EMAIL
  **Automated Emails:**
  • Milestone notifications
  • Estimate delivery
  • Status updates
  • Professional templates
end note

note right of DB
  **Core Data Models:**
  • Users (Contractors)
  • Leads (Prospects)
  • Jobs (Projects)
  • Estimates + Line Items
  • Progress Photos
  • Email Notifications
end note

note bottom of PHOTO
  **Key Automation:**
  50% time reduction in estimates
  Automated client communication
  Visual progress tracking
  Professional presentations
end note

@enduml